<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>go off on someone • go off someone</xh5><p> <i>go off on someone</i>—(UK coll.) become very angry or excited: Your hair color is nice, I wish I could dye my hair like that. My parents will <u>go off on</u> me though.</p><p> <i>go off someone</i>—(coll.) cease to like a person: Earlier on in the episode the two were cuddling up in the pub, so why has she <u>gone off</u> him so soon?</p> </entry>
